{
  "message": "Add fuzz target for glob_match pattern matching\n\nStructure-aware fuzz target covering:\n- Raw byte patterns and strings\n- Structured patterns with literals, wildcards, character classes, ranges, escapes\n- Invariant assertions (star matches anything, empty pattern only matches empty)\n\nIncludes 25 seed corpus files covering common patterns, edge cases, and escapes.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
